      </metadata>
   </prolog>
   <refbody>
      <section>
         <note type="note">Your processing
system will provide a run-time flag or parameter to cause the content of this
element to be specially displayed for draft output only. By default, it is
stripped out to prevent publishing internal comments by mistake!.</note>
